title: Camp WeWow Under the Sea Week Day 2
description:
It's Under the Sea Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're exploring our imaginations and writing our own original sea stories! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/activity-write-a-collaborative-sea-story for directions to today's activity! Then, share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share! And don't forget to call us at 1-888-7WOW-WOW to share your sea story for the chance to be featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire this Friday!

See Privacy Policy at https://art19.com/privacy and California Privacy Notice at https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info.
